  <chunk id="9a8ffdaee3a800f0e6867b63ffd109e9c30621b8.c2" text="The study was conducted according to Preferred Reporting Items for Systematic Reviews and Meta-Analyses checklist and selected randomized control trials which compared the efficacy of glucocorticoids add-on to macrolide in the treatment of MRMP in children.">
